---
title: Speedy BBQ Chicken Sandwiches with Dill Pickle Coleslaw
description: Super quick and full of flavour, these sandwiches are packed with classic BBQ punch! Sweet and smoky BBQ sauce smothers quick-to-broil diced chicken. Dill pickles add zesty tang to every bite.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/speedy-bbq-chicken-sandwiches-18deb453-5650c8c3.jpg
